    <item>
      <title>“神秘举动”导致土耳其里拉下跌，随后市场恢复平静</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/-mystery-move-triggers-turkish-lira-losses-before-calm-returns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[早盘交易期间，土耳其里拉突然短暂暴跌，令交易员们摸不着头脑，纷纷止损，但随后，该货币才稳定在更为可预测的走势上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/-mystery-move-triggers-turkish-lira-losses-before-calm-returns</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 08:45:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
